dc_title_s: Assiscunk Creek to Old River Road along the Delaware River
dc_description_s: Map shows exterior wharf line, old wooden bulkhead, new wooden bulkhead, old foundry wharf, and a partly-filled area not considered a bulkhead. Map also depicts the new stone wall, the high water line of 1876, and the properties of A. H. McNeal and the McNeal Pipe and Foundry Company.
